## 📥 Supported Input

<!-- BEGIN AUTO-GENERATED README SUPPORTED INPUT -->
- OpenAPI 3 (YAML/JSON)
- AsyncAPI (YAML/JSON)
- JSON Schema
- MCP tool schemas
- XML Schema (XSD)
- Protocol Buffers / gRPC (`.proto`)
- Apache Avro schema (AVSC)
- JSON data
- YAML data
